# Migrations

- Add a new numbered SQL file: `drizzle/00NN_descriptive_name.sql` (use the next sequence number after the latest in `drizzle/`).
- Update `src/db/schema.ts` to reflect schema changes.
- Do not modify migrations that may already be applied in production — add a new migration instead.
- After schema changes, run `npm run db:migrate` locally and ensure related tests pass.

## Related

- Archived migrations live under `drizzle/_archive/` — do not revive without explicit intent.
- Platform plan config may mirror to `.dinaya/plans.json` in local dev (gitignored runtime data).
